<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Application Received</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #8B5CF6; color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .content { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 30px; background-color: #8B5CF6; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .info-box { background-color: white; border: 2px solid #8B5CF6; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🎉 New Application Received!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi {{employerName}},</h2>
            <p>Great news! You have received a new application for your job posting.</p>
            
            <div class="info-box">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Application Details</h3>
                <p><strong>Job Title:</strong> {{jobTitle}}</p>
                <p><strong>Applicant:</strong> {{applicantName}}</p>
                <p><strong>Date Applied:</strong> {{currentYear}}</p>
            </div>
            
            <p>Login to your dashboard to review the application, view the candidate's profile, and take action.</p>
            
            <a href="{{appUrl}}/employer/applications" class="button">Review Application</a>
            
            <p>Don't miss out on great talent! Review applications promptly to stay ahead.</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>The {{appName}} Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} {{appName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
